Description: This episode with Guthi and Palak trying to sell bangles and see Ramu selling Samosas. Unable to sell anything, they rush inside where Kapil's concert starts on the stage. After the concert, Guthi, Palak and Ramu walk on the stage and try to sell their goods. Kapil drives the three off the stage. Later, Kapil invites Priyanka Chopra on the stage for the promotion of her new movie, Mary Kom. Watch the episode and have a blast.
